name: Listened to Dear Internet Episode 47: Gimme that soup goo

content.html:
Dear Internet, This weeks episode is all about what to do with a bunch of sushi. You can’t just let it go bad can you?? That’s worse than eating it all in one sitting even though it was meant for a whole party. We also talk about the worst soup and getting in trouble with the misses for sexy orc pics. Stay gold, XOXO We are a new show, and would greatly appreciate if you could leave us a 5-star review on your podcast app of choice! If you want more Dear Internet, please consider supporting us on patreon through Dear Internet. Sincerely, The coHosts- Nick Bristow, Jennifer Cheek, Michael DiMauro, and Tim Lanning! Apple Podcast, Spotify, RSS – follow us on Twitter!

By Dear Internet
